## ðŸ”§ Troubleshooting

### "Not a git repository"

Make sure you're in a Git repository. Initialize with:
```bash
git init
```

### "No changes to commit"

Stage your changes first or let ai-commit do it automatically.

### "Notion token not provided" (if using Notion plugin)

Set environment variables in `.env`:
```bash
NOTION_TOKEN=secret_xxxxx
NOTION_DATABASE_ID=xxxxx
```

